==職業生涯==
===亞利桑那響尾蛇===
哈根斯在[[2009年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2009年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]的第六輪被響尾蛇隊選走。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sun|first1=Chhun|title=Former Pitman ace set for Arizona|url=http://www.turlockjournal.com/archives/107/|website=turlockjournal.com|publisher=Turlock (Calif.) Journal|accessdate=August 18, 2014|date=June 27, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814102826/http://www.turlockjournal.com/archives/107/|archive-date=August 14, 2014}}</ref>他在2014年8月14日登上大聯盟。他只在大聯盟出賽2場比賽，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/Dbacks/status/501416750919872512 |title=Twitter / Dbacks: #Dbacks recall pitcher @willharris15 from the Triple-A Reno @Aces and option pitcher Bradin Hagens to Reno. |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2016-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406104547/https://twitter.com/dbacks/status/501416750919872512 |dead-url=no }}</ref>留下1敗，防禦率3.38的成績。

===坦帕灣光芒===
2015年4月4日，他被交易至光芒。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2015/04/minor-moves-hagens-owens-castillo.html|title=Minor Moves: Tomas, Oliver, Brignac, Zito, White, LaHair, Capps|last1=Polishuk|first1=Mark|last2=Johnson|first2=Brad|work=mlbtraderumors.com|date=April 4, 2015|accessdate=April 5, 2015|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019154745/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2015/04/minor-moves-hagens-owens-castillo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他在同年的11月6日成為自由球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/milb/stats/stats.jsp?sid=milb&t=l_trn&lid=117|title=International League Transactions|page=November 2015|work=milb.com|accessdate=November 7, 2015|archive-date=2019-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209080649/http://www.milb.com/milb/stats/stats.jsp?sid=milb&t=l_trn&lid=117|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===廣島東洋鯉魚===
2016年，哈根斯加盟日職的廣島東洋鯉魚。[https://web.archive.org/web/20160818021234/http://www.carp.co.jp/team16/member/p66.html]

===再回響尾蛇===
2018年2月16日，哈根斯第二次和響尾蛇隊簽約。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-transaction-feb-16-22-2018/#UuFppx7HQGw04vZM.97 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2018-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180302050116/https://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/minor-league-transaction-feb-16-22-2018/#UuFppx7HQGw04vZM.97 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在11月3日成為自由球員。

===法戈紅鷹===
2019年4月1日，哈根斯與美國職協的法戈紅鷹隊簽下合約。

===三返響尾蛇===
2019年5月20日，響尾蛇隊又買下哈根斯的合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.americanassociationbaseball.com/redhawks-hagens-heading-back-to-diamondbacks-organization/|title=Redhawks' Hagens Heading Back to Diamondbacks Organization|date=May 20, 2019|accessdate=May 20, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125052728/https://www.americanassociationbaseball.com/redhawks-hagens-heading-back-to-diamondbacks-organization/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在11月7日成為自由球員。

===再回紅鷹===
2020年3月18日，哈根斯再度與紅鷹隊簽下合約。

===樂天桃猿===
2020年12月30日，哈根斯加盟中職的樂天桃猿，中文登錄名為「豪勁」。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/GOCPBL/status/1344167562637012994|title=Rakuten Monkeys have signed Deck McGuire and Bradin Hagens as their foreign players for the 2021 CPBL season.|date=December 30, 2020|accessdate=December 30, 2020|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230065539/https://twitter.com/GOCPBL/status/1344167562637012994|dead-url=no}}</ref>

